# Faiss Project Rules

## Building

Always build faiss using the `helper-build.sh` script at the repo root. Never run cmake/make commands directly.

```bash
./helper-build.sh
```

## Code Changes

When modifying code, preserve all existing comments that still apply after the change. Only remove a comment if it is made entirely obsolete or incorrect by the new code.
